<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="meanwhile-adv">meanwhile <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'miːnwaɪl/    美 /'miːnwaɪl/  </p>
<p><a href="meantime">非正式用语</a></p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[句子副词] 与此同时；在此期间：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Mother went shopping; meanwhile, I cleaned the house. 
妈妈去买东西，与此同时，我打扫房间。</p></div></div>